    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM7.4">
<l>kaḷini lāveḻil matipurai mukamuṅ kaṇṇa ṉētiṇkai mārvuntiṇ ṭōḷum</l>
<l>taḷirma larkkaruṅ kuḻalpiṟai yatuvum taṭaṅkoḷ tāmaraik kaṇkaḷum polinta</l>
<l>viḷamai yiṉpattai yiṉṟeṉṟaṉ kaṇṇāṟ paruku vēṟkivaḷ tāyeṉa niṉainta</l>
<l>vaḷaviṟ piḷḷaimai yiṉpattai yiḻanta pāvi yēṉeṉa tāvinil lātē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Kṛṣṇa!</l>
<l>The breath of me – who am a sinner, who am now drinking with my own eyes</l>
<l rend="indent">the joy of [Your] youth which shines</l>
<l rend="indent">with a face like the beautiful full moon with delightful moonlight,</l>
<l rend="indent">strong shoulders, chest, and strong arms,</l>
<l rend="indent">that crescent moon[-like forehead underneath]</l>
<l rend="indent">the black curly hair with blooming flowers, large lotus eyes,</l>
<l>[but] who have lost the endless joy of [Your] childhood</l>
<l rend="indent">which knows [nothing but] that ‘she is [my] mother’ –</l>
<l>shall not remain.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
